\langle f, g \rangle_{\mathcal{H}_R} := \int_{-\infty}^R f(x) \bar{g}(x) dx + \int_R^{\infty} \frac{1-\phi^2(x)}{1 - \phi^2(R)} f(x) \bar{g}(x) dx
